Dubai, United Arab Emirates
Organisation Process Review and Mapping
Posted: 1 day, 23 hours ago
We are looking for someone to review and document all of the processes within our Operations. From Retail to Warehousing, HR and Finance, to Head Office and Events.
We require someone who is highly experienced in process re-engineering / review, documentation, mapping and business consulting.
Ideally someone with a lean background who can make recommendations for areas of improvement.
To be completed onsite in our Head Office in Oud Metha, our Warehouse in Jebel Ali and Retail Stores in Dubai.
Location:
Applicant is required to be in United Arab Emirates
Start date:05/18/2014
Skills needed:
Lean Management,
Business Process Management Consultant,
Business Process Management ,
Process Improvement,
Process Documentation,
Business Process Reengineering,
Lean Six Sigma Black Belt,
Business Analysis,
Business Consulting,
Internal Communications,
Kaizen
Budget: $2,000 - $5,000
Prerequisites
Required
Optional
Attach CV
In United Arab Emirates
Work on-site
